{"tid":1678920,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"勇武，文宣，經濟戰全部都有作用，最緊要唔好放棄","createTime":"2019-10-28T01:57:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-04T13:38:13.000Z","uid":40250,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"fee8bb2a8ed6f605e384c94c247f08f0f1f6db9d","tid":1678920,"uid":40250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T01:57:29.000Z","msg":"勇武剩番唔多，就謹慎行動主力裝修，麻包袋<br />\n<br />\n文宣俾人捉晒dum落海，就請大家做多一步，係社區每一吋地方都做文宣，唔一定貼之前貼開既地方<br />\n<br />\n返工一定要，自問唔想睇住香港一日一日咁俾陰乾，保持團火搵到錢就盡量搵渠道幫行動組既人<br />\n<br />\n香港人已經退無可退，唔好由得事情惡化，變得冷漠逆來順受"},{"pid":"8d310e8745eda365d29fa82793f497cdd2c6d689","tid":1678920,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T01:57:54.000Z","msg":"可唔可以唔好剩係懲罰出名嘅黃店？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1675556\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1675556</a>"},{"pid":"e10f19604eb1bc4725d1d929eb86d4762c108fcd","tid":1678920,"uid":835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T02:08:43.000Z","msg":"每一環都重要，齊上齊落呀屌你個閪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"987d36aefc8daae75f07d836373e9a4cebb72504","tid":1678920,"uid":40250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T03:03:59.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"869fc81598f5e9ffc163a455862c7c02a3577f16","tid":1678920,"uid":40250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T08:12:44.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"58b9f2533292a630c70b942ab02e8a357c06fffc","tid":1678920,"uid":40250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T02:59:08.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2e020a3c60eaac35d1bfc7f49300b2b4cc097911","tid":1678920,"uid":265766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T03:53:22.000Z","msg":"非常同意.  積少成多就會找到缺口"},{"pid":"2b9634893373a3484414fc63988ca3224818a356","tid":1678920,"uid":40250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T11:28:07.0